title: #241 Dose Folks
description:
It's a reverberating Tuesday as Joe recovers from major oral surgery to get into his cigar & drunk frat guy filled trip to Ann Arbor while Mark goes to the worst cajun restaurant in all of Ohio! Check it out!

We're doing a LIVE pod with special guests at the Village Underground in NYC on May 7th! Reserve tickets here: www.comedycellar.com/
